title: National Lampoons University Tycoon-MONEY
description:
GAME INFORMATION:
 -------------------
 
  The Dean quit and you're in charge! Can you build the ultimate university?
  This is your chance to set the bar for all schools. Ultimate success is
  measured by the dollars you earn and your global stats -- coolness, party
  rating, and reputation! Are you a campus stud or a campus dud? Includes 20
  awesome missions and game script written by National Lampoon's comedy team
